        SHIF Compliant ‚Ä¢ Housing Levy Ready
      </div>

      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 mb-6 leading-[1.1] tracking-tight">
        The Gold Standard for <br />
        <span class="text-gradient">Kenyan Payroll.</span>
      </h1>
      
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 mb-10 leading-relaxed max-w-4xl mx-auto font-medium">
        Don't risk penalties. An end-to-end HR platform that automates <strong>Complex Payrolls</strong>, <strong>Statutory Returns</strong>, <strong>Staff Loans</strong>, and <strong>Performance Appraisals</strong>.
      </p>

      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-4 mb-16">
        <a href="#payroll" class="bg-cyan-700 text-white px-10 py-5 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg hover:bg-cyan-800 transition-all shadow-xl shadow-cyan-900/10">
          View Payroll Features
        </a>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn-secondary px-10 py-5 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg transition-all">
